# Blitz
Android AR shooter game
Description: 
This is an Android AR shooter game, the name says it all!
for this game, players will download this app and install it on their phones
set up the server and get ready to play!
use your phone as a gun and aim at your friends to cause them damage using the camera
enemies will be damaged once they're in your crosshairs
go nuts!
This game uses AR, streaming and a new positioning algorithm that I invented, works well for 2d flatspace
Read my paper on this!(should you know chinese, it could be easy to find lol)
